<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MANDA A VISAO ⚡</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #09090b;
            --accent: #6d28d9; 
            --accent-glow: rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.4);
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-dim: #a1a1aa;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: var(--text-main);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
        }

        /* Fundo Mesh Gradient */
        .mesh-bg {
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            z-index: 0;
            background: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 10% 20%, rgba(109, 40, 217, 0.2) 0%, transparent 40%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 90% 80%, rgba(29, 78, 216, 0.15) 0%, transparent 40%);
        }

        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 420px;
        }

        /* Quadro Principal (Glassmorphism) */
        .main-card {
            background: var(--glass);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 32px;
            padding: 40px 24px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px -12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
        }

        .header-group {
            margin-bottom: 32px;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: -1.5px;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #ffffff, #a1a1aa);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        }

        p {
            color: var(--text-dim);
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        form {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 16px;
        }

        /* Caixa de texto */
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 150px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 18px;
            color: #ffffff;
            font-size: 1rem;
            resize: none;
            outline: none;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        textarea:focus {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-color: var(--accent);
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        textarea::placeholder {
            color: #52525b;
        }

        /* Botão de Enviar */
        button {
            width: 100%;
            background: #ffffff;
            color: #09090b;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 18px;
            padding: 16px;
            font-size: 1.05rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 8px;
            transition: all 0.2s ease;
        }

        button:hover {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px var(--accent-glow);
        }

        button svg {
            width: 18px;
            height: 18px;
        }

        /* Tags do Rodapé */
        .footer-tags {
            margin-top: 24px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 8px;
        }

        .tag {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            padding: 6px 12px;
            border-radius: 100px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .tag-anon {
            color: #4ade80;
            background: rgba(74, 222, 128, 0.1);
        }

        .tag-filtro {
            color: #60a5fa;
            background: rgba(96, 165, 250, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="mesh-bg"></div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="main-card">
            <div class="header-group">
                <h1>MANDA A VISAO</h1>
                <p>Escreva sua duvida real sobre Jesus</p>
            </div>
            
            <form action="https://formspree.io/f/xykvjdbj" method="POST">
                <textarea 
                    name="duvida_do_jovem" 
                    placeholder="manda o papo... o que vc sempre quis perguntar sobre jesus mas nunca teve coragem?" 
                    required></textarea>
                    
                <button type="submit">
                    enviar agora
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="22" y1="2" x2="11" y2="13"></line><polygon points="22 2 15 22 11 13 2 9 22 2"></polygon></svg>
                </button>
            </form>

            <div class="footer-tags">
                <span class="tag tag-anon">100% anônimo</span>
                <span class="tag tag-filtro">sem filtro</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
